title: Guns N Roses - Covers The Others 2017 320ak
description:
Guns N Roses - Covers The Others 2017 320ak

I found a copy of this from awhile back but saw the need to give it my treatment so 
I did. I added 5 tracks to it and reduced it from a FLAC share to a 320ak.
So enjoy and share with others real loud you must do.
